{"tid":1382104,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［教條主義］暫時讓勇武休息 讓和理飛重新出發","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:22.000Z","uid":93327,"like":105,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"54d18958071bce5b5806b6c8145ee8de299ad623","tid":1382104,"uid":93327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiifsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=dba8893e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n重點可以由2:48聽 有關教條主義<br />\n<br />\n我認為而家勇武已經去到一個樽頸位 暫時再勇武只會令到義士送頭 亦令到香港人麻木了警暴濫權<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得應該安排和理非全面進場 可以繼續舉行機場集會 暫時應該最合適亦最有成效 亦都可以暫停地區光復行動 集中五大訴求 每星期在機場自遊行<br />\n<br />\n勇武過去已經有大量義士被捕 而且藍黃支持者已經歸邊 警黑合作明顯 再勇武只會助長濫捕<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後，香港人加油</strong>"},{"pid":"40302fa08323b989f96bffd0ac2899e9c68db9bd","tid":1382104,"uid":8948,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"下轉應該係和理非出場，靜坐，等佢出晒防暴ready<br />\n跟住發覺對住和理非，唔知點清場"},{"pid":"13521e31928f6536e473352f0e82a7222e7eacfd","tid":1382104,"uid":93327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"45a167ad0b5d0ef4a6fb11a12bb25828b0b2f489","tid":1382104,"uid":93327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"和理飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f87c6e3d1dbf369d41b92066acffe98c3c4619","tid":1382104,"uid":93327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"和理飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5187dba8592e84a89a6ea2dd5309a1f169d502","tid":1382104,"uid":93327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"和理飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=